results.title: Grilled Shrimp Skewers with Green Tahini Sauce

steps.step: Place all ingredients in blender and process until combined, and desired smoothness. Season to taste with salt.
Toss shrimp with olive oil and season with salt and pepper. Arrange on skewers.
Grill for 2 minutes on each side until the shrimp is pink, and cooked through.
Serve with Green Tahini Sauce on the side.

results.title: Massaged Kale and Brussels Sprouts Salad with Tahini-Maple Dressing

steps.step: In a large bowl, combine the chopped kale and sliced brussels sprouts; toss well.In a 2 cup liquid measuring cup or small bowl, whisk together the ingredients for the dressing; pour over the kale and brussels sprouts and using your hands, massage the dressing into the salad to distribute thoroughly and to tenderize the vegetables.
Sprinkle the salad with the almonds and Parmesan and toss just before serving.
